com.itko.lisa.coordinator

Interface ServiceManagerSupport

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CoordinatorServer, SimulatorServer, TestRegistry

    public interface ServiceManagerSupport
    Classes the implement this interface are able to be remotely controlled.
